ZH: 社区是一个有着共同利益的团体。
EN: The community is a group with common interests.

ZH: 社区里有许多不同的家庭和个人。
EN: There are many different families and individuals in the community.

ZH: 社区的发展取决于每个人的贡献。
EN: The development of the community depends on the contributions of everyone.

ZH: 在我们的社区里有一个公园和一家小学。
EN: In our community, there is a park and an elementary school.

ZH: 社区活动可以增进邻里之间的合作。
EN: Community activities can promote cooperation among neighbors.

ZH: 我们的社区有一个定期的清洁活动。
EN: Our community has a regular cleaning activity.

ZH: 社区中的人们通常会互相帮助。
EN: People in the community usually help each other.

ZH: 我们的社区正在计划一个夏季派对。
EN: Our community is planning a summer party.

ZH: 在紧急情况下，社区可以团结起来。
EN: In case of emergency, the community can come together.

ZH: 社区警察在保护社区安全方面做出了很多贡献。
EN: Community police have made a lot of contributions to ensuring community safety.

ZH: 社区图书馆是一个重要的文化资源。
EN: The community library is an important cultural resource.

ZH: 社区商店提供各种各样的商品和服务。
EN: Community shops offer a variety of goods and services.

ZH: 社区医疗中心提供基本的医疗服务。
EN: Community health centers provide basic medical services.

